{"source": "enwiki", "kind": "wikipedia_lead", "title": "Wantoe Teah Wantoe", "pageid": 81701637, "rev_id": 1333751457, "timestamp": "2026-01-19T15:23:14Z", "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wantoe_Teah_Wantoe", "text": "Wantoe Teah Wantoe (born December 24, 1994) is a Liberian scholar, youth rights advocate, and student leader known for his work in education reform, children's rights, diaspora youth mobilization, and his leadership roles at the University of Oxford.", "images": []}
