{"source": "enwiki", "kind": "wikipedia_lead", "title": "2026 Indonesia Air Transport ATR 42 crash", "pageid": 82138878, "rev_id": 1333751710, "timestamp": "2026-01-19T15:24:56Z", "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2026_Indonesia_Air_Transport_ATR_42_crash", "text": "On 17 January 2026, an ATR 42 operated by Indonesia Air Transport crashed while flying from Adisutjipto Airport to Sultan Hasanuddin International Airport in Indonesia. Air traffic control reportedly lost contact with the flight in the South Sulawesi area, and the aircraft was ultimately found to have crashed in the Bulusaraung mountain area. All ten people on board were killed. Burning wreckage was found in a remote area.\n\nThe incident resulted a large search and rescue operation that involved the National Search and Rescue Agency , AirNav Indonesia, Indonesian Air Force , the local government, and surrounding community.", "images": [{"file_title": "File:Aviacionavion.png", "url": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/68/Aviacionavion.png", "mime": "image/png", "width": 1600, "height": 1600, "size_bytes": 241701}, {"file_title": "File:Flag of Indonesia.svg", "url": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/9/9f/Flag_of_Indonesia.svg", "mime": "image/svg+xml", "width": 900, "height": 600, "size_bytes": 148}, {"file_title": "File:PK-THT (cropped).jpg", "url": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/0e/PK-THT_%28cropped%29.jpg", "mime": "image/jpeg", "width": 4731, "height": 3032, "size_bytes": 6863418}, {"file_title": "File:PK-THT crash site 2.jpg", "url": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/30/PK-THT_crash_site_2.jpg", "mime": "image/jpeg", "width": 1599, "height": 898, "size_bytes": 163035}]}
{"source": "enwiki", "kind": "wikipedia_lead", "title": "ONE Fight Night 39", "pageid": 81750838, "rev_id": 1333751733, "timestamp": "2026-01-19T15:25:01Z", "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ONE_Fight_Night_39", "text": "ONE Fight Night 39: Rambolek vs. Dayakaev was a combat sports event produced by ONE Championship that took place on January 24, 2026, at Lumpinee Boxing Stadium in Bangkok , Thailand.", "images": [{"file_title": "File:Yin and Yang symbol.svg", "url": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3c/Yin_and_Yang_symbol.svg", "mime": "image/svg+xml", "width": 250, "height": 250, "size_bytes": 507}, {"file_title": "File:Yin and Yang.svg", "url": "https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3c/Yin_and_Yang_symbol.svg", "mime": "image/svg+xml", "width": 250, "height": 250, "size_bytes": 507}]}
